CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 28 reads: " Free Prizes, Samples and Demonstrations Galore...12. Mrs. Protho awarding an electric fryer, a grand prize from the Marnell Company, to Mrs. Marjorie Jackson...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Protho wearing striped dress, presenting an electric fryer Mrs. Marjorie Jackson on stage with Norge Appliances display in Syria Mosque at the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
